Neil S. Novich



Mr. Neil S. Novich is on the Board of Directors at Linear Technology Corp., Beacon Roofing Supply, Inc., Hillenbrand, Inc., Analog Devices, Inc., W.W. Grainger, Inc. and The Field Museum of Natural History. Mr. Novich was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Ryerson, Inc. and a Trustee by Children's Home + Aid. He also served on the board at Bain & Co., Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Harvard University and a graduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology.



